reviews.title: Atmospheric and tasteful
reviews.text: Highly recommended. Through the beautiful terrace you reach the entrance. A picture of an establishment when you walk in. Were quickly addressed and could choose a spot. A mix of sofas and chairs in beautiful colors. Dressed with rugs. A nice bar and the toilet was even a picture. The food was more than good. So tasteful and beautifully served. Not from a simple plate, but nice in baskets and pans. Friendly staff, friendly staff. Because of a stomach reduction I can't eat much. An appetizer became a main course. This was also taken into account which is very pleasant. Highly recommended all in all!

reviews.title: Very pleasantly surprised!
reviews.text:
Nice place and we really ate very well there. The carpaccio was very good and the main course was also top notch.

Compared to other restaurants on the square, the Poelier is much better! We will definitely be back again.

reviews.title: Have a nice night out 😀
reviews.text:
Good food! Diverse menu, certainly not just chicken.  Delicious cauliflower steak and tasty salad. 
Friendly, helpful service and stylish decor!
Highly recommended.

reviews.title: Delicious food
reviews.text: Delicious food in an attractive restaurant. The asparagus with ham and hollandaise sauce were exquisite. As dessert enjoyed the coupe lawyer. Homemade lawyer, super tasty! And the service is very friendly, professional and attentive. We come here all the time.

reviews.title: Cozy and tasteful!
reviews.text: Delicious food at De Poelier! The atmosphere was cozy and the food super delicious – lots of choice and everything good to taste. The service was friendly and attentive. Really a nice place for dinner as a couple. We will definitely be back!

reviews.title: Enjoyed it!!
reviews.text: Greatly enjoyed with the family. Plenty of choice for everyone. A cozy and warm atmosphere. The service is also very friendly. We will definitely be back!!

reviews.title: Top restaurant!
reviews.text: Super good food with friends. Service was friendly and the delicious food and good service have made for a super positive experience!! We're definitely coming to dinner more often.

reviews.title: Poelier review
reviews.text: It was a nice restaurant. You have a lot of choice on the menu and the restaurant is nice and central. Service is good and fast. We will definitely be back more often!

reviews.title: Top tent
reviews.text: We have eaten here with some friends delicious also the friendly service is a good addition 3 course surprise menu is recommended

reviews.title: Best restaurant in Epe
reviews.text: Beautiful restaurant in the heart of Epe good menu lots of diversity and excellent service. Would definitely recommend to visit!

reviews.title: Super!
reviews.text: Super good experience had here! Great food, the cooks clearly know what they are doing, also super helpful and charming service, definitely recommended!

reviews.title: Surprising in Epe!
reviews.text: This Foodbar is definitely recommended. Beautiful, tasteful and creative dishes. Super fresh and delicious bread which is made by yourself. Where do you find that?! All this in a cozy, atmosphereville atmosphere with friendly and helpful staff! We liked the 4 course surprise menu very much. Beautiful dishes with seasonal ingredients. Served in a creative and unique jacket! Recommended! We will definitely be back soon!

reviews.title: Chicken next level in a completely styled environment with top service
reviews.text: Top service, style inside is really great down to the toilet styled. And then the food: fresh, creative and pure. And then that half chicken with potatoes, that really is chicken next level. But the pulled chicken is also a feast in your mouth, both texture and taste are really great. Highly recommended!
